sentence: The GuruFocus All-in-One Screener can be used to find insider trades from the past week.
Under the Insiders tab, change the settings for All Insider Buying to "$200,000+," the duration to "June 2017" and "May 2017" and All Insider Sales to "$5,000,000+."
